---
title: Steak-Spiced Burgers with Disco Fries
description: Introducing disco fries, the New Jersey cousin of Montreal poutine! These crispy, golden DIY fries are coated in melty cheddar instead of cheese curds and a healthy smothering of spiced gravy. Let's face it: you can't have a burger without fries; with tonight's meal, you get the best of both!
